('Meta Front-End Developer Professional Certificate', 'Meta (via Coursera)', 'https://www.coursera.org/professional-certificates/meta-front-end-developer', 'Software Engineering', 'beginner', 'freemium', '5-7 months', '["HTML", "CSS", "JavaScript", "React"]'::jsonb, 'Built by Meta engineers; covers the practical front-end stack most junior roles ask for.'),
